===========
FlowStrider
===========

.. image:: https://gitlab.com/dlr-dw/automated-threat-modeling/flowstrider/badges/main/pipeline.svg
  :target: https://gitlab.com/dlr-dw/automated-threat-modeling/flowstrider/-/pipelines
